config TEST_BLOAT_SIZE
	int "Padding array size in bytes to inflate the binary"
	default 0
	help
	  Size of a const padding array linked into .rodata.
	  Used to push the signed image close to or beyond the
	  slot size limit for testing the MCUboot image size check.

source "Kconfig.zephyr"
